<title>
[The use of antioxidants for the correction of coronary risk factors in patients with myocardial ischemia].
</title>

<text>

<abstract>
The investigation of influent of soy isoflavones and vitamin-antioxidants on lipid spectrum of blood, coronary risk factors and indexes of antioxidant status in patients with ischemic heart disease. Observation has shown, that the use in the diet-therapy in patients with ischemic heart disease of soy isoflavones and vitamin-antioxidants is rather perspective.
</abstract>

</text>
